snippet.title: Nintendo Switch Redout Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
NEXT GENERATION RACING COMING TO THE NINTENDO SWITCH!! Redout is a tribute to the old racing monsters such as F-Zero, WipeOut, Rollcage.

Published by Nicalis, Inc., Redout will release on Nintendo Switch in Spring 2017 at retail and digitally via the Nintendo eShop.
